<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ cóng yuǎn fāng zhī dào nǐ, nǐ cóng yuǎn fāng zhī dào wǒ.
 wǒ men tóng yǒu yī kē zhēn chéng de xīn, shēn shēn de ài zhōng guó.
 nà lǐ de hé chǎng dà, nà lǐ de mín zú duō,
 qiān qiān wàn wàn qīn ài de tóng bāo, zài qī dài zhe nǐ wǒ.
 lái ba, wǒ men jǔ qǐ shǒu, zhù fú zhōng guó.
 ràng shén de líng zì yóu yùn xíng, bǎ zhòng è dǎ pò.
 ràng wǒ men de jiǎo bù, kě yǐ zǒu xiàng liè guó.
 yuàn dì xiōng de shēn shàng, bù zài yǒu jiā suǒ.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ cóng yuǎn fāng zhī dào nǐ 迦南796</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
